{
  "video_id": "twG4mr6Jov0",
  "title": "What you can do to prevent Alzheimer's | Lisa Genova",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12937.0,
      "end_time": 17351.0,
      "text": "How many people here would like to live to be at least 80 years old?"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17892.0,
      "end_time": 19367.0,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19391.0,
      "end_time": 22186.0,
      "text": "I think we all have this hopeful expectation"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 22210.0,
      "end_time": 24170.0,
      "text": "of living into old age."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24648.0,
      "end_time": 26734.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s project out into the future,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 26758.0,
      "end_time": 28317.0,
      "text": "to your future \"you&#39;s,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 28342.0,
      "end_time": 31195.0,
      "text": "and let&#39;s imagine that we&#39;re all 85."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 31714.0,
      "end_time": 33732.0,
      "text": "Now, everyone look at two people."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 34971.0,
      "end_time": 38503.0,
      "text": "One of you probably has Alzheimer&#39;s disease."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 39185.0,
      "end_time": 42609.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 42633.0,
      "end_time": 44227.0,
      "text": "Alright, alright."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 44774.0,
      "end_time": 48591.0,
      "text": "And maybe you&#39;re thinking, \"Well, it won&#39;t be me.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 49170.0,
      "end_time": 52555.0,
      "text": "Then, OK. You are a caregiver."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 53208.0,
      "end_time": 54372.0,
      "text": "So --"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 54396.0,
      "end_time": 57268.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 57292.0,
      "end_time": 58649.0,
      "text": "so in some way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 58673.0,
      "end_time": 62317.0,
      "text": "this terrifying disease is likely to affect us all."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 62753.0,
      "end_time": 65767.0,
      "text": "Part of the fear around Alzheimer&#39;s stems from the sense"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 65791.0,
      "end_time": 68205.0,
      "text": "that there&#39;s nothing we can do about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 68229.0,
      "end_time": 73354.0,
      "text": "Despite decades of research, we still have no disease-modifying treatment"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 73378.0,
      "end_time": 74685.0,
      "text": "and no cure."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 75141.0,
      "end_time": 77610.0,
      "text": "So if we&#39;re lucky enough to live long enough,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 77634.0,
      "end_time": 80742.0,
      "text": "Alzheimer&#39;s appears to be our brain&#39;s destiny."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 81189.0,
      "end_time": 83680.0,
      "text": "But maybe it doesn&#39;t have to be."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 83405.0,
      "end_time": 86770.0,
      "text": "What if I told you we could change these statistics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 86794.0,
      "end_time": 89484.0,
      "text": "literally change our brain&#39;s destiny,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 89508.0,
      "end_time": 93360.0,
      "text": "without relying on a cure or advancements in medicine?"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 93803.0,
      "end_time": 96328.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s begin by looking at what we currently understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 96352.0,
      "end_time": 98709.0,
      "text": "about the neuroscience of Alzheimer&#39;s."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 99550.0,
      "end_time": 102559.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s a picture of two neurons connecting."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 102583.0,
      "end_time": 105940.0,
      "text": "The point of connection, this space circled in red,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 105964.0,
      "end_time": 107603.0,
      "text": "is called the synapse."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 107627.0,
      "end_time": 110818.0,
      "text": "The synapse is where neurotransmitters are released."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 110843.0,
      "end_time": 115111.0,
      "text": "This is where signals are transmitted, where communication happens."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 115135.0,
      "end_time": 120241.0,
      "text": "This is where we think, feel, see, hear, desire ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 120265.0,
      "end_time": 121914.0,
      "text": "and remember."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 121938.0,
      "end_time": 124836.0,
      "text": "And the synapse is where Alzheimer&#39;s happens."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 124860.0,
      "end_time": 126822.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s zoom in on the synapse"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 126846.0,
      "end_time": 129933.0,
      "text": "and look at a cartoon representation of what&#39;s going on."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 130619.0,
      "end_time": 132906.0,
      "text": "During the business of communicating information,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 132930.0,
      "end_time": 136928.0,
      "text": "in addition to releasing neurotransmitters like glutamate into the synapse,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 136952.0,
      "end_time": 141413.0,
      "text": "neurons also release a small peptide called amyloid beta."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 142437.0,
      "end_time": 147421.0,
      "text": "Normally, amyloid beta is cleared away metabolized by microglia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 147445.0,
      "end_time": 149597.0,
      "text": "the janitor cells of our brains."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 150225.0,
      "end_time": 154840.0,
      "text": "While the molecular causes of Alzheimer&#39;s are still debated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 154108.0,
      "end_time": 157362.0,
      "text": "most neuroscientists believe that the disease begins"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 157386.0,
      "end_time": 160216.0,
      "text": "when amyloid beta begins to accumulate."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 160787.0,
      "end_time": 163536.0,
      "text": "Too much is released, or not enough is cleared away,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 163560.0,
      "end_time": 166894.0,
      "text": "and the synapse begins to pile up with amyloid beta."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 166918.0,
      "end_time": 169137.0,
      "text": "And when this happens, it binds to itself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 169161.0,
      "end_time": 172450.0,
      "text": "forming sticky aggregates called amyloid plaques."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 173402.0,
      "end_time": 176355.0,
      "text": "How many people here are 40 years old or older?"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 177400.0,
      "end_time": 179524.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re afraid to admit it now."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 179548.0,
      "end_time": 181774.0,
      "text": "This initial step into the disease,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 181798.0,
      "end_time": 184882.0,
      "text": "this presence of amyloid plaques accumulating,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 184906.0,
      "end_time": 187500.0,
      "text": "can already be found in your brains."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 188910.0,
      "end_time": 191561.0,
      "text": "The only way we could be sure of this would be through a PET scan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 191585.0,
      "end_time": 195401.0,
      "text": "because at this point, you are blissfully unaware."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 195425.0,
      "end_time": 199714.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re not showing any impairments in memory, language, or cognition ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 199738.0,
      "end_time": 200889.0,
      "text": "yet."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 201291.0,
      "end_time": 205828.0,
      "text": "We think it takes at least 15 to 20 years of amyloid plaque accumulation"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 205852.0,
      "end_time": 208233.0,
      "text": "before it reaches a tipping point,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 208257.0,
      "end_time": 210492.0,
      "text": "then triggering a molecular cascade"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 210516.0,
      "end_time": 213183.0,
      "text": "that causes the clinical symptoms of the disease."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 213630.0,
      "end_time": 215591.0,
      "text": "Prior to the tipping point,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 215615.0,
      "end_time": 219199.0,
      "text": "your lapses in memory might include things like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 219223.0,
      "end_time": 221548.0,
      "text": "\"Why did I come in this room?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 221572.0,
      "end_time": 223800.0,
      "text": "or \"Oh ... what&#39;s his name?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 224299.0,
      "end_time": 226643.0,
      "text": "or \"Where did I put my keys?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 227373.0,
      "end_time": 229929.0,
      "text": "Now, before you all start freaking out again,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 229953.0,
      "end_time": 235351.0,
      "text": "because I know half of you did at least one of those in the last 24 hours --"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 235375.0,
      "end_time": 238612.0,
      "text": "these are all normal kinds of forgetting."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 238636.0,
      "end_time": 240948.0,
      "text": "In fact, I would argue that these examples"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 240973.0,
      "end_time": 242950.0,
      "text": "might not even involve your memory,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 242974.0,
      "end_time": 245866.0,
      "text": "because you didn&#39;t pay attention to where you put your keys"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 245890.0,
      "end_time": 247234.0,
      "text": "in the first place."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 247259.0,
      "end_time": 248936.0,
      "text": "After the tipping point,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 248961.0,
      "end_time": 252484.0,
      "text": "the glitches in memory, language and cognition are different."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 252508.0,
      "end_time": 255408.0,
      "text": "Instead of eventually finding your keys in your coat pocket"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 255432.0,
      "end_time": 257433.0,
      "text": "or on the table by the door,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 257458.00000000003,
      "end_time": 260172.00000000003,
      "text": "you find them in the refrigerator,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 260196.00000000003,
      "end_time": 262162.0,
      "text": "or you find them and you think,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 262186.0,
      "end_time": 263719.0,
      "text": "\"What are these for?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 264663.0,
      "end_time": 269871.0,
      "text": "So what happens when amyloid plaques accumulate to this tipping point?"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 269895.0,
      "end_time": 273214.0,
      "text": "Our microglia janitor cells become hyper-activated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 273238.0,
      "end_time": 277372.0,
      "text": "releasing chemicals that cause inflammation and cellular damage."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 277396.0,
      "end_time": 279991.0,
      "text": "We think they might actually start clearing away"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 280150.0,
      "end_time": 281719.0,
      "text": "the synapses themselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 282218.0,
      "end_time": 286666.0,
      "text": "A crucial neural transport protein called \"tau\" becomes hyperphosphorylated"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 286690.0,
      "end_time": 289274.0,
      "text": "and twists itself into something called \"tangles,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 289298.0,
      "end_time": 292333.0,
      "text": "which choke off the neurons from the inside."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 292357.0,
      "end_time": 296191.0,
      "text": "By mid-stage Alzheimer&#39;s, we have massive inflammation and tangles"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 296215.0,
      "end_time": 298162.0,
      "text": "and all-out war at the synapse"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 298186.0,
      "end_time": 299438.0,
      "text": "and cell death."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 300580.0,
      "end_time": 303146.0,
      "text": "So if you were a scientist trying to cure this disease,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 303170.0,
      "end_time": 306167.0,
      "text": "at what point would you ideally want to intervene?"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 306954.0,
      "end_time": 310858.0,
      "text": "Many scientists are betting big on the simplest solution:"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 310882.0,
      "end_time": 314716.0,
      "text": "keep amyloid plaques from reaching that tipping point,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 314740.0,
      "end_time": 318768.0,
      "text": "which means that drug discovery is largely focused on developing a compound"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 318792.0,
      "end_time": 324140.0,
      "text": "that will prevent, eliminate, or reduce amyloid plaque accumulation."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 324679.0,
      "end_time": 329868.0,
      "text": "So the cure for Alzheimer&#39;s will likely be a preventative medicine."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 329892.0,
      "end_time": 333320.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re going to have to take this pill before we reach that tipping point,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 333345.0,
      "end_time": 335597.0,
      "text": "before the cascade is triggered,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 335621.0,
      "end_time": 338649.0,
      "text": "before we start leaving our keys in the refrigerator."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 339201.0,
      "end_time": 342874.0,
      "text": "We think this is why, to date, these kinds of drugs have failed"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 342898.0,
      "end_time": 344135.0,
      "text": "in clinical trials --"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 344159.0,
      "end_time": 346604.0,
      "text": "not because the science wasn&#39;t sound,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 346628.0,
      "end_time": 350762.0,
      "text": "but because the people in these trials were already symptomatic."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 350786.0,
      "end_time": 352518.0,
      "text": "It was too late."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 352542.0,
      "end_time": 355794.0,
      "text": "Think of amyloid plaques as a lit match."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 355818.0,
      "end_time": 359236.0,
      "text": "At the tipping point, the match sets fire to the forest."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 359704.0,
      "end_time": 361654.0,
      "text": "Once the forest is ablaze,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 361678.0,
      "end_time": 364160.0,
      "text": "it doesn&#39;t do any good to blow out the match."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 364184.0,
      "end_time": 367707.0,
      "text": "You have to blow out the match before the forest catches fire."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 368151.0,
      "end_time": 370140.0,
      "text": "Even before scientists sort this out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 370380.0,
      "end_time": 372906.0,
      "text": "this information is actually really good news for us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 372930.0,
      "end_time": 376974.0,
      "text": "because it turns out that the way we live can influence the accumulation"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 376998.0,
      "end_time": 378227.0,
      "text": "of amyloid plaques."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 378251.0,
      "end_time": 379827.0,
      "text": "And so there are things we can do"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 379851.0,
      "end_time": 382470.0,
      "text": "to keep us from reaching that tipping point."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 382937.0,
      "end_time": 386825.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s picture your risk of Alzheimer&#39;s as a see-saw scale."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 386849.0,
      "end_time": 388897.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re going to pile risk factors on one arm,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 388922.0,
      "end_time": 391400.0,
      "text": "and when that arm hits the floor, you are symptomatic"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 391424.0,
      "end_time": 393359.0,
      "text": "and diagnosed with Alzheimer&#39;s."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 393878.0,
      "end_time": 396597.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s imagine you&#39;re 50 years old."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 396621.0,
      "end_time": 398356.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re not a spring chicken anymore,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 398380.0,
      "end_time": 401452.0,
      "text": "so you&#39;ve accumulated some amyloid plaques with age."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 401476.0,
      "end_time": 403667.0,
      "text": "Your scale is tipped a little bit."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 404143.0,
      "end_time": 405881.0,
      "text": "Now let&#39;s look at your DNA."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 406356.0,
      "end_time": 409908.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve all inherited our genes from our moms and our dads."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 409932.0,
      "end_time": 414100.0,
      "text": "Some of these genes will increase our risk and some will decrease it."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 414340.0,
      "end_time": 416223.0,
      "text": "If you&#39;re like Alice in \"Still Alice,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 416247.0,
      "end_time": 420798.0,
      "text": "you&#39;ve inherited a rare genetic mutation that cranks out amyloid beta,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 420822.0,
      "end_time": 424375.0,
      "text": "and this alone will tip your scale arm to the ground."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 424399.0,
      "end_time": 428565.0,
      "text": "But for most of us, the genes we inherit will only tip the arm a bit."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 428589.0,
      "end_time": 433404.0,
      "text": "For example, APOE4 is a gene variant that increases amyloid,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 433428.0,
      "end_time": 436695.0,
      "text": "but you can inherit a copy of APOE4 from mom and dad"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 436720.0,
      "end_time": 439111.0,
      "text": "and still never get Alzheimer&#39;s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 439135.0,
      "end_time": 441248.0,
      "text": "which means that for most of us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 441272.0,
      "end_time": 445111.0,
      "text": "our DNA alone does not determine whether we get Alzheimer&#39;s."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 445804.0,
      "end_time": 447277.0,
      "text": "So what does?"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 447302.0,
      "end_time": 451940.0,
      "text": "We can&#39;t do anything about getting older or the genes we&#39;ve inherited."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 451118.0,
      "end_time": 454115.0,
      "text": "So far, we haven&#39;t changed our brain&#39;s destiny."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 454964.0,
      "end_time": 456429.0,
      "text": "What about sleep?"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 457980.0,
      "end_time": 461180.0,
      "text": "In slow-wave deep sleep, our glial cells rinse cerebral spinal fluid"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 461204.0,
      "end_time": 462420.0,
      "text": "throughout our brains,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 462444.0,
      "end_time": 466160.0,
      "text": "clearing away metabolic waste that accumulated in our synapses"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 466400.0,
      "end_time": 467941.0,
      "text": "while we were awake."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 467965.0,
      "end_time": 470770.0,
      "text": "Deep sleep is like a power cleanse for the brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 471466.0,
      "end_time": 474652.0,
      "text": "But what happens if you shortchange yourself on sleep?"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 475241.0,
      "end_time": 476772.0,
      "text": "Many scientists believe"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 476797.0,
      "end_time": 481470.0,
      "text": "that poor sleep hygiene might actually be a predictor of Alzheimer&#39;s."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 481433.0,
      "end_time": 486359.0,
      "text": "A single night of sleep deprivation leads to an increase in amyloid beta."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 487230.0,
      "end_time": 490656.0,
      "text": "And amyloid accumulation has been shown to disrupt sleep,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 490680.0,
      "end_time": 493167.0,
      "text": "which in turn causes more amyloid to accumulate."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 493191.0,
      "end_time": 495667.0,
      "text": "And so now we have this positive feedback loop"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 495691.0,
      "end_time": 498563.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s going to accelerate the tipping of that scale."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 499126.0,
      "end_time": 500549.0,
      "text": "What else?"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 500573.0,
      "end_time": 502198.0,
      "text": "Cardiovascular health."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 502863.0,
      "end_time": 506608.0,
      "text": "High blood pressure, diabetes, obesity, smoking, high cholesterol,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 506632.0,
      "end_time": 510768.0,
      "text": "have all been shown to increase our risk of developing Alzheimer&#39;s."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 510792.0,
      "end_time": 512683.0,
      "text": "Some autopsy studies have shown"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 512707.0,
      "end_time": 515379.0,
      "text": "that as many as 80 percent of people with Alzheimer&#39;s"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 515403.0,
      "end_time": 518164.0,
      "text": "also had cardiovascular disease."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 518188.0,
      "end_time": 523193.0,
      "text": "Aerobic exercise has been shown in many studies to decrease amyloid beta"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 523217.0,
      "end_time": 524948.0,
      "text": "in animal models of the disease."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 525439.0,
      "end_time": 529190.0,
      "text": "So a heart-healthy Mediterranean lifestyle and diet"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 529430.0,
      "end_time": 531697.0,
      "text": "can help to counter the tipping of this scale."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 532517.0,
      "end_time": 534866.0,
      "text": "So there are many things we can do"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 534890.0,
      "end_time": 537262.0,
      "text": "to prevent or delay the onset of Alzheimer&#39;s."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 537286.0,
      "end_time": 539515.0,
      "text": "But let&#39;s say you haven&#39;t done any of them."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 540310.0,
      "end_time": 542484.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s say you&#39;re 65;"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 542509.0,
      "end_time": 546175.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s Alzheimer&#39;s in your family, so you&#39;ve likely inherited a gene or two"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 546199.0,
      "end_time": 548223.0,
      "text": "that tips your scale arm a bit;"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 548247.0,
      "end_time": 550978.0,
      "text": "you&#39;ve been burning the candle at both ends for years;"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 551300.0,
      "end_time": 552506.0,
      "text": "you love bacon;"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 552530.0,
      "end_time": 554752.0,
      "text": "and you don&#39;t run unless someone&#39;s chasing you."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 554777.0,
      "end_time": 556780.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 556102.0,
      "end_time": 559714.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s imagine that your amyloid plaques have reached that tipping point."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 559738.0,
      "end_time": 561786.0,
      "text": "Your scale arm has crashed to the floor."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 561810.0,
      "end_time": 563491.0,
      "text": "You&#39;ve tripped the cascade,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 563515.0,
      "end_time": 565810.0,
      "text": "setting fire to the forest,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 565105.0,
      "end_time": 568203.0,
      "text": "causing inflammation, tangles, and cell death."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 568957.0,
      "end_time": 571616.0,
      "text": "You should be symptomatic for Alzheimer&#39;s."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 571640.0,
      "end_time": 574956.0,
      "text": "You should be having trouble finding words and keys"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 574980.0,
      "end_time": 578126.0,
      "text": "and remembering what I said at the beginning of this talk."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 578737.0,
      "end_time": 580451.0,
      "text": "But you might not be."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 581000.0,
      "end_time": 583478.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s one more thing you can do to protect yourself"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 583502.0,
      "end_time": 586880.0,
      "text": "from experiencing the symptoms of Alzheimer&#39;s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 586112.0,
      "end_time": 590603.0,
      "text": "even if you have the full-blown disease pathology ablaze in your brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 590627.0,
      "end_time": 594534.0,
      "text": "It has to do with neural plasticity and cognitive reserve."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 595810.0,
      "end_time": 597458.0,
      "text": "Remember, the experience of having Alzheimer&#39;s"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 597482.0,
      "end_time": 600688.0,
      "text": "is ultimately a result of losing synapses."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 601159.0,
      "end_time": 604536.0,
      "text": "The average brain has over a hundred trillion synapses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 604560.0,
      "end_time": 607272.0,
      "text": "which is fantastic; we&#39;ve got a lot to work with."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 607297.0,
      "end_time": 608966.0,
      "text": "And this isn&#39;t a static number."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 608990.0,
      "end_time": 611388.0,
      "text": "We gain and lose synapses all the time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 611412.0,
      "end_time": 614215.0,
      "text": "through a process called neural plasticity."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 614239.0,
      "end_time": 616311.0,
      "text": "Every time we learn something new,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 616335.0,
      "end_time": 620462.0,
      "text": "we are creating and strengthening new neural connections,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 620486.0,
      "end_time": 622103.0,
      "text": "new synapses."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 622808.0,
      "end_time": 624383.0,
      "text": "In the Nun Study,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 624407.0,
      "end_time": 629300.0,
      "text": "678 nuns, all over the age of 75 when the study began,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 629324.0,
      "end_time": 631632.0,
      "text": "were followed for more than two decades."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 631657.0,
      "end_time": 635117.0,
      "text": "They were regularly given physical checkups and cognitive tests,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 635141.0,
      "end_time": 639189.0,
      "text": "and when they died, their brains were all donated for autopsy."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 639213.0,
      "end_time": 643588.0,
      "text": "In some of these brains, scientists discovered something surprising."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 643612.0,
      "end_time": 648188.0,
      "text": "Despite the presence of plaques and tangles and brain shrinkage --"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 648212.0,
      "end_time": 651810.0,
      "text": "what appeared to be unquestionable Alzheimer&#39;s --"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 651105.0,
      "end_time": 654784.0,
      "text": "the nuns who had belonged to these brains showed no signs"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 654808.0,
      "end_time": 657375.0,
      "text": "of having the disease while they were alive."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 658100.0,
      "end_time": 659449.0,
      "text": "How can this be?"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 659829.0,
      "end_time": 663955.0,
      "text": "We think it&#39;s because these nuns had a high level of cognitive reserve,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 663980.0,
      "end_time": 667903.0,
      "text": "which is a way of saying that they had more functional synapses."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 667927.0,
      "end_time": 670501.0,
      "text": "People who have more years of formal education,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 670525.0,
      "end_time": 672760.0,
      "text": "who have a high degree of literacy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 672784.0,
      "end_time": 676363.0,
      "text": "who engage regularly in mentally stimulating activities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 676387.0,
      "end_time": 678867.0,
      "text": "all have more cognitive reserve."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 678892.0,
      "end_time": 683190.0,
      "text": "They have an abundance and a redundancy in neural connections."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 683430.0,
      "end_time": 685723.0,
      "text": "So even if they have a disease like Alzheimer&#39;s"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 685747.0,
      "end_time": 687800.0,
      "text": "compromising some of their synapses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 687825.0,
      "end_time": 690810.0,
      "text": "they&#39;ve got many extra backup connections,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 690834.0,
      "end_time": 694169.0,
      "text": "and this buffers them from noticing that anything is amiss."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 694797.0,
      "end_time": 697590.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s imagine a simplified example."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 697830.0,
      "end_time": 699809.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s say you only know one thing about a subject."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 699833.0,
      "end_time": 701362.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s say it&#39;s about me."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 701386.0,
      "end_time": 703692.0,
      "text": "You know that Lisa Genova wrote \"Still Alice,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 703716.0,
      "end_time": 706152.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s the only thing you know about me."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 706176.0,
      "end_time": 708566.0,
      "text": "You have that single neural connection,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 708590.0,
      "end_time": 710536.0,
      "text": "that one synapse."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 710560.0,
      "end_time": 712720.0,
      "text": "Now imagine you have Alzheimer&#39;s."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 712745.0,
      "end_time": 715780.0,
      "text": "You have plaques and tangles and inflammation"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 715102.0,
      "end_time": 717837.0,
      "text": "and microglia devouring that synapse."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 718423.0,
      "end_time": 722653.0,
      "text": "Now when someone asks you, \"Hey, who wrote &#39;Still Alice?&#39;\""
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 722677.0,
      "end_time": 723922.0,
      "text": "you can&#39;t remember,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 723946.0,
      "end_time": 727129.0,
      "text": "because that synapse is either failing or gone."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 727153.0,
      "end_time": 728912.0,
      "text": "You&#39;ve forgotten me forever."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 729580.0,
      "end_time": 732206.0,
      "text": "But what if you had learned more about me?"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 732230.0,
      "end_time": 734319.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s say you learned four things about me."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 734343.0,
      "end_time": 736188.0,
      "text": "Now imagine you have Alzheimer&#39;s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 736212.0,
      "end_time": 739207.0,
      "text": "and three of those synapses are damaged or destroyed."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 739897.0,
      "end_time": 742358.0,
      "text": "You still have a way to detour the wreckage."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 742382.0,
      "end_time": 744401.0,
      "text": "You can still remember my name."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 745103.0,
      "end_time": 749290.0,
      "text": "So we can be resilient to the presence of Alzheimer&#39;s pathology"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 749530.0,
      "end_time": 752156.0,
      "text": "through the recruitment of yet-undamaged pathways."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 752180.0,
      "end_time": 755959.0,
      "text": "And we create these pathways, this cognitive reserve,"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 755983.0,
      "end_time": 757683.0,
      "text": "by learning new things."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 758275.0,
      "end_time": 762795.0,
      "text": "Ideally, we want these new things to be as rich in meaning as possible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 762820.0,
      "end_time": 767559.0,
      "text": "recruiting sight and sound and associations and emotion."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 768218.0,
      "end_time": 771353.0,
      "text": "So this really doesn&#39;t mean doing crossword puzzles."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 771377.0,
      "end_time": 775473.0,
      "text": "You don&#39;t want to simply retrieve information you&#39;ve already learned,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 775498.0,
      "end_time": 778841.0,
      "text": "because this is like traveling down old, familiar streets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 778865.0,
      "end_time": 781450.0,
      "text": "cruising neighborhoods you already know."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 781933.0,
      "end_time": 784766.0,
      "text": "You want to pave new neural roads."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 784791.0,
      "end_time": 787303.0,
      "text": "Building an Alzheimer&#39;s-resistant brain"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 787327.0,
      "end_time": 789507.0,
      "text": "means learning to speak Italian,"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 789531.0,
      "end_time": 791400.0,
      "text": "meeting new friends,"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 791650.0,
      "end_time": 792232.0,
      "text": "reading a book,"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 792256.0,
      "end_time": 794625.0,
      "text": "or listening to a great TED Talk."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 795103.0,
      "end_time": 800415.0,
      "text": "And if, despite all of this, you are someday diagnosed with Alzheimer&#39;s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 800440.0,
      "end_time": 803593.0,
      "text": "there are three lessons I&#39;ve learned from my grandmother"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 803617.0,
      "end_time": 807353.0,
      "text": "and the dozens of people I&#39;ve come to know living with this disease."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 807935.0,
      "end_time": 811118.0,
      "text": "Diagnosis doesn&#39;t mean you&#39;re dying tomorrow."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 811143.0,
      "end_time": 812865.0,
      "text": "Keep living."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 812889.0,
      "end_time": 815255.0,
      "text": "You won&#39;t lose your emotional memory."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 815279.0,
      "end_time": 818785.0,
      "text": "You&#39;ll still be able to understand love and joy."
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 818809.0,
      "end_time": 821812.0,
      "text": "You might not remember what I said five minutes ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
